      "value": "صنم يوناني قديمة"
    },
    "bn": {
      "language": "bn",
      "value": "গ্রিক আইন-কানুনের দেবী"
    },
    "ca": {
      "language": "ca",
      "value": "deessa grega, padrona de la justícia i de la llei"
    },
    "cs": {
      "language": "cs",
      "value": "řecká bohyně"
    },
    "de": {
      "language": "de",
      "value": "Titanin in der griechischen Mythologie"
    },
    "el": {
      "language": "el",
      "value": "τιτάνας της Ελληνικής μυθολογίας, προσωποποίηση της φυσικής και ηθικής τάξης, και της εθιμοτυπίας"
    },
    "en": {
      "language": "en",
      "value": "in ancient Greek mythology, a titaness, the personification of divine order, fairness, law, natural law, and custom, whose symbols are the scales of justice"
    },
